sQuestion: There are 1986 books in Oak Grove 's public library . In addition , there are 5106 books in its school libraries . How many books do the libraries in Oak Grove have overall ?

A farmer estimates that he will harvest 48097 bushels of wheat . The weather is perfect during the growing season , so he harvests 684 bushels of wheat than expected . How many bushels of wheat does the farmer harvest ?
